/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T15:08:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇下有沒人/ 車用<br />\n考慮serviceability ，如果漏水比人投訴到仆街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T02:49:34.000Z","msg":"本人外行人，想問下幾時會係雨水流落下面，幾時會係地下水湧上嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T02:51:31.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64eace5b312444514e2e83a61b7ef80489ec459d","tid":1132614,"uid":185631,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T02:53:42.000Z","msg":"首先你要知道其實普通石屎(concrete)本身其實係有防水的作用<br />\n但係個問題係石屎本身設計是抵禦壓力, 所以compressive strength好強<br />\n之不過石屎自己又容易裂, 所以長久以來都要做防水去保護石屎<br />\n<br />\n只於什麼地方需要做防水就其實因人而異<br />\n有人用的地方, 例如商住工廈, 地下停車場, 我們就會跟據容易入水的位置做防水, 例如天台、外牆、廁所、地牢。當然你見村屋可以完全唔做防水，但當人對居住環境有要求，就自然有防水的需要。<br />\n<br />\n至於地牢點解要，係因為地牢例如停車場的牆身好多時有油漆、就算冇油漆，長期漏水都會導致發霉、蚊蟲滋生、甚至石屎老化加快。所以做防水其實係保護建築物，尤其石屎，不會因為入水，導致鋼筋生銹，加快老化。"},{"pid":"d9831956ac0e1fc13b6bbc65c252a354e06cc6c3","tid":1132614,"uid":115613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64eace5b312444514e2e83a61b7ef80489ec459d","tid":1132614,"uid":185631,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T02:53:42.000Z","msg":"首先你要知道其實普通石屎(concrete)本身其實係有防水的作用<br />\n但係個問題係石屎本身設計是抵禦壓力, 所以compressive strength好強<br />\n之不過石屎自己又容易裂, 所以長久以來都要做防水去保護石屎<br />\n<br />\n只於什麼地方需要做防水就其實因人而異<br />\n有人用的地方, 例如商住工廈, 地下停車場, 我們就會跟據容易入水的位置做防水, 例如天台、外牆、廁所、地牢。當然你見村屋可以完全唔做防水，但當人對居住環境有要求，就自然有防水的需要。<br />\n<br />\n至於地牢點解要，係因為地牢例如停車場的牆身好多時有油漆、就算冇油漆，長期漏水都會導致發霉、蚊蟲滋生、甚至石屎老化加快。所以做防水其實係保護建築物，尤其石屎，不會因為入水，導致鋼筋生銹，加快老化。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T03:11:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />知唔知幾時用噴果種防水"},{"pid":"9ed2873762daf5aea39092c9b73174a0ad18bca1","tid":1132614,"uid":36994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T03:27:01.000Z","msg":"石屎都有分防水石屎 WP/ CAL藥水<br />\n通常落水缺 天面 露台<br />\n<br />\n另外通常申勤位 水錶房 pump房都要做防水<br />\n<br />\n唔好問點解 叫你做就做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0133b07ab5653aa4f093c1f0648533af606b1620","tid":1132614,"uid":139907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f85c4d9d7d577c11b781461bd385c138d90f535e","tid":1132614,"uid":115613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T12:13:24.000Z","msg":"其實waterproofing material 係咪只用係substructure<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但好似馬路咁點解唔洗做防水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T04:04:38.000Z","msg":"露天位(bal./canopy/planter/ramp/泳池/天面/cutrain wall邊/框邊)<br />\n室內(sunken/水缸)<br />\netc.大把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8aebb82bd309ef563173d124c14a9983be85a79","tid":1132614,"uid":190035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae086501d59753ca02ff81e7523e15fc5c561db1","tid":1132614,"uid":93043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1ce513a6804688732af1ed822c010a9e9a4e123","tid":1132614,"uid":190035,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f85c4d9d7d577c11b781461bd385c138d90f535e","tid":1132614,"uid":115613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T12:13:24.000Z","